## G6PD multiplexed functional assay
This repository includes the code and files neeed to create figures from Geck et al. 2025

## Citation

Please cite: Geck RC et al. 2025. Functional evidence for G6PD variant classification from mutational scanning. bioRxiv. doi: https://doi.org/10.1101/2025.08.11.669723

## Repository overview

The script to analyze data and generate all figures is G6PD_MultiplexedFunctionalAssay_Analysis.Rmd.
All other files are called by the script.
We recommend downloading the entire folder (Geck2025_G6PD_MultiplexedFunctionalAssay) and running the script with that folder set as the working directory.
Three files will need to be unzipped after downloading.
